********************************* PETIT AMI PROJECT ****************************

Please see the following documents to get started in Petit-Ami

doc/petit_ami.docx	The "grand unified" document of what it is, how to install
                    it, etc.
INSTALL				The basic install procedure.

The project is presented as a complete within a single tree. The format is
along the lines of GNU projects, IE, with a configure, Makefile, README, etc.